ca.ualberta.cmput301f20t04.bookatmenow

Class Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cmput301f20t04.bookatmenow.Book

  • public class Book
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a book in the app. Is owned by one user, has title, author, status (Available, Requested, Accepted, Borrowed), has a unique ISBN. Can be borrowed by one user, have multiple requests on it. Can have an image.
